{"id":230024,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":6,"day":14}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"俄语周刊","column":"","genre":"","count":"136","ytitle":"","mtitle":"永远记着吧","ftitle":"","authors":["M·依萨柯夫斯基","蒋建锟"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"M·依萨柯夫斯基"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(蒋建锟译)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论你往那里走，何处行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但在这里要停留，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向这敬爱的墓地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"致以衷心的敬礼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论你是谁——渔夫，鑛工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学者或牧人——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远记着:这里躺着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你最好的朋友。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了你，也为了我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他做了一切他所能做的:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战斗中奋不顾身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫祖国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>&lt;img=516e070501&gt;</FONT>"}]}